{"product_id":"black-dry-fit-vest","title":"BLACK DRY-FIT VEST","description":"\u003cp\u003eLightweight Fabric. Slim Fit. Sleeveless Vest. 100% Recycled Polyester. Dry Fit Performance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis slim-fit Dry Fit vest is designed for comfort and performance across all athletic activities. Crafted from lightweight recycled polyester, it feels soft against the skin while allowing maximum airflow and unrestricted movement. The moisture-wicking Dry Fit fabric helps keep you dry and comfortable during workouts, training sessions, and active routines. Finished with a clean, minimal silhouette, this vest delivers a sleek athletic look while supporting high-performance wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash with similar colors in cold water. Avoid fabric softeners to maintain moisture-wicking performance. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLightweight recycled polyester fabric for breathability and comfort. Slim fit for a close-to-body, performance-ready feel. Sleeveless design for enhanced airflow and freedom of movement. Dry Fit technology helps manage moisture during any athletic activity. True to size—recommended to order your usual size.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47064627839130,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47064627871898,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47064627904666,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47064627937434,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00748copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440848","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/black-dry-fit-vest","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}